\frac{A^{2}}{\tau}\intop_{0}^{\tau}\frac{e^{j\Omega t}-e^{-j\Omega t}}{2j}\cdot\frac{e^{j\Omega\left(t-\lambda\right)}-e^{-j\Omega\left(t-\lambda\right)}}{2j}\mathrm{d}t
